doc.previous: In 2011, additional terminal space was added and existing terminals were refreshed as part of a $543 million expansion project.[13] A new Terminal C with six additional gates was built along with dedicated commuter gate areas in the new Terminal C and new commuter facilities in Terminal A. A new parking lot C was added along with additional support facilities such as a Central Utility plant.
